<div class="flex min-h-screen bg-gray-50 p-4">
  <!-- 왼쪽: 폼 + 힌트 -->
  <main class="w-2/3 pr-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-8">
     <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">SQL Injection 연습</h2>
     <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">데이터베이스 보안 취약점 탐색</p>
      <form action="/lesson/sql_injection/query" method="get" class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <label for="username" class="block text-gray-700 mb-1">Username</label>
          <input
            id="username"
            name="username"
            type="text"
            placeholder="admin을 입력해 보세요."
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:border-blue-300"
          />
        </div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
        >
          검색
        </button>
      </form>

      <!-- 힌트 토글 -->
      <div class="mt-6 text-center">
        <button
          id="hint-btn"
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-yellow-400 text-yellow-900 rounded hover:bg-yellow-500 transition"
        >
          힌트 보기
        </button>
      </div>
      <div
        id="hint-box"
        class="hidden mt-4 p-4 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 rounded text-sm space-y-2"
      >
        <p>▶ SQL Injection을 위해, WHERE 절의 <code class="bg-yellow-200 px-1 rounded">&lt;username&gt;</code> 부분에 어떻게 해야 할까요? </p>
        <pre class="bg-yellow-200 p-2 rounded whitespace-pre-wrap break-words overflow-auto">
작은따옴표'와 AND,OR 연산자를 이용해 보세요.
        </pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- 오른쪽: SQL 구문 -->
  <aside class="w-1/3 pl-4 sticky top-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">실습용 SQL 구문</h3>
      <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-sm">
SELECT id, username, password
FROM users
WHERE username = '&lt;username&gt;';
      </pre>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-xs">
        &lt;username&gt; 부분에 입력한 값이 직접 들어갑니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>

<script>
  document.getElementById('hint-btn').addEventListener('click', function() {
    const box = document.getElementById('hint-box');
    if (box.classList.contains('hidden')) {
      box.classList.remove('hidden');
      this.textContent = '힌트 숨기기';
    } else {
      box.classList.add('hidden');
      this.textContent = '힌트 보기';
    }
  });
</script>